# Configuring Grafana

## Exporting Metrics to Grafana

- Log into Grafana: http://yourserver:3000 with admin Credentials.
- Click on Settings Icon and head to Data Sources. 
- Choose Prometheus as a Data Source, enter your Prometheus Server Details and click on Save & Test.
- Upon Verification, your Prometheus Server will be added as a Data Source.


## Importing Dashboards

- Go to Dashboards > Import.
- Paste and Upload the JSON files and click on Import.
- Configure Variables from Settings according to your requirements.